Our usual carpet cleaner wasn't available, so I gave Brimley's White Glove a try. VERY glad I chose them.   A lot of carpet cleaners bait-and-switch you with "free" deals only to charge you a fortune once they get done. Others hire shady characters who barely look able to function a vacuum cleaner let alone shampoo your carpets.  Brimley's technician (Steve) was extremely professional, polite, helpful and thorough. He gave of all kinds of options but didn't pressure us. Highly recommend their service.

